===Etymology===
Literally: The tree may prefer calm but the wind keeps blowing.
===Proverb===
{{cmn-proverb|t|pin=shù yù jìng ér fēng bù zhĭ|pint=shu4yu4jing4er2feng1bu4zhi3|tra=樹欲靜而風不止|sim=树欲静而风不止|rs=木12}}
#  The objective laws often go counter to man's desires.
